[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":794},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":771,"related:\u002Fcss\u002F20200517\u002F168089779\u002F":780},"\u002Fen\u002Fcss\u002F2020\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcss-design-patterns-oocss\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":756,"date":757,"description":18,"extension":758,"lang":759,"meta":760,"navigation":331,"path":761,"readingMinutes":762,"seo":763,"standalone":764,"stem":765,"tags":766,"tldr":768,"updated":768,"url":769,"__hash__":770},"content\u002FCSS\u002F淺談-CSS-設計模式系列-OOCSS-篇.md","淺談 CSS 設計模式系列-OOCSS 篇","168089779",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":749},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,36,39,42,84,87,91,94,263,287,393,399,422,425,429,432,435,498,501,575,593,607,728,731,734,745],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"OOCSS 是 CSS 設計模式的另一種，其中最主要代表的框架就是 Bootstrap。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"oocss","OOCSS",[16,24,25],{},"OOCSS 全名是 「Object Oriented CSS」，中文的意思大概是「物件導向 CSS」，另一種中文翻譯是「面向對象 CSS」，其主要設計理念為兩者",[27,28,29,33],"ul",{},[30,31,32],"li",{},"Separation of content from container - 內容與容器的分離",[30,34,35],{},"Separation of structure from skin - 結構與樣式的分離",[16,37,38],{},"透過這兩個設計裡面可以大大增加 CSS 的擴充性以及 CSS 彈性，因此只要你有使用過 Bootstrap，那麼你就已經在無形中學習了 OOCSS 因為 Bootstrap 就是採用 OOCSS 設計，簡單來講就是每一個 class 他都可以獨立的運作。",[16,40,41],{},"舉例來講你不需要懂 CSS 你只需要看手冊，你就可以使用 Bootstrap 來套用樣式",[43,44,49],"pre",{"className":45,"code":46,"language":47,"meta":48,"style":48},"language-html shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","\u003Ch1 class=\"text-left text-danger d-flex\">這是一個 h1\u003C\u002Fh1>\n","html","",[50,51,52],"code",{"__ignoreMap":48},[53,54,57,61,65,69,72,76,79,81],"span",{"class":55,"line":56},"line",1,[53,58,60],{"class":59},"s8XSl","\u003C",[53,62,64],{"class":63},"syv7_","h1",[53,66,68],{"class":67},"sK3KL"," class",[53,70,71],{"class":59},"=",[53,73,75],{"class":74},"sWayO","\"text-left text-danger d-flex\"",[53,77,78],{"class":59},">這是一個 h1\u003C\u002F",[53,80,64],{"class":63},[53,82,83],{"class":59},">\n",[16,85,86],{},"因此 OOCSS 的設計裡面每一個 class 都是一個可以直接使用的 CSS 獨立個體，在這邊其實也與 SMACSS 的 Module 非常雷同。",[12,88,90],{"id":89},"separation-of-content-from-container-內容與容器的分離","Separation of content from container (內容與容器的分離)",[16,92,93],{},"在「內容與容器的分離」中有一個重點觀念，不要被排版版型限制，所謂被排版版型限制的意思如下方程式碼",[43,95,99],{"className":96,"code":97,"language":98,"meta":48,"style":48},"language-scss shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast",".header {\n  color: yellow;\n  width: 50px;\n  height: 50px;\n}\n.content {\n  color: red;\n  width: 50x;\n  height: 50px;\n}\n.footer {\n  color: blue;\n  width: 50px;\n  height: 50px;\n}\n","scss",[50,100,101,109,125,142,156,162,170,182,194,207,212,220,232,245,258],{"__ignoreMap":48},[53,102,103,106],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,104,105],{"class":67},".header",[53,107,108],{"class":59}," {\n",[53,110,112,116,119,122],{"class":55,"line":111},2,[53,113,115],{"class":114},"stw71","  color",[53,117,118],{"class":59},": ",[53,120,121],{"class":114},"yellow",[53,123,124],{"class":59},";\n",[53,126,128,131,133,136,140],{"class":55,"line":127},3,[53,129,130],{"class":114},"  width",[53,132,118],{"class":59},[53,134,135],{"class":114},"50",[53,137,139],{"class":138},"sOudu","px",[53,141,124],{"class":59},[53,143,145,148,150,152,154],{"class":55,"line":144},4,[53,146,147],{"class":114},"  height",[53,149,118],{"class":59},[53,151,135],{"class":114},[53,153,139],{"class":138},[53,155,124],{"class":59},[53,157,159],{"class":55,"line":158},5,[53,160,161],{"class":59},"}\n",[53,163,165,168],{"class":55,"line":164},6,[53,166,167],{"class":67},".content",[53,169,108],{"class":59},[53,171,173,175,177,180],{"class":55,"line":172},7,[53,174,115],{"class":114},[53,176,118],{"class":59},[53,178,179],{"class":114},"red",[53,181,124],{"class":59},[53,183,1